{
  "info": {
    "name": "RoadResQ API v4 — Complete",
    "description": "RoadResQ API v4.1.0 — Base URL: https://api-h6acdw3itq-ww.a.run.app\n\n🔐 AUTH: All protected routes need: Authorization: Bearer <Firebase ID Token>\nGet token from Firebase Auth (client SDK), pass to /api/auth/login to verify.\n\nFlows:\n1. Register → POST /api/auth/register (email+password creates Firebase+Firestore)\n2. Login   → POST /api/auth/login { idToken } — verifies Firebase token\n3. Profile → GET /api/auth/me (Bearer token required)\n4. Jobs    → POST /api/jobs with optional scheduledPickupDate/Time\n5. Quotes  → POST /api/quotes with preferredDate/Time\n6. Garage  → POST /api/garage-requests with preferredDate/Time\n7. Cancel  → DELETE /api/jobs/:id/cancel with cancellationReason",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "4.1.0"
  },
