  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔑 Get Firebase Token (Testing Helper)",
      "description": "Use this to get a real Firebase ID token for Postman testing.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Sign In with Firebase (get idToken)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "https://identitytoolkit.googleapis.com/v1/accounts:signInWithPassword?key=AIzaSyDgQXxBGq6nXMJlGI0xaRhYqOmWmPGQxYE",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@1234\",\n  \"returnSecureToken\": true\n}"
            },
            "description": "⚠️ Replace the API key in the URL with the actual Firebase Web API Key.\nFind it: Firebase Console → Project Settings → General → Web API Key\n\nAfter running this:\n1. Copy idToken from the response\n2. Set it as {{idToken}} variable in your Postman environment\n3. Use it as: Authorization: Bearer {{idToken}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (Email + Password)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ahmed Al-Rashidi\",\n  \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@1234\",\n  \"phone\": \"+974-5555-0001\",\n  \"role\": \"customer\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Creates Firebase Auth account + Firestore user document.\nrole: customer | driver | admin | garage\n\nReturns: { uid, name, email, phone, role, createdAt }"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register Driver",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Mohammed Al-Qahtani\",\n  \"email\": \"driver@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Driver@1234\",\n  \"phone\": \"+974-5555-0099\",\n  \"role\": \"driver\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Register as driver role. Then POST /api/drivers to create driver profile."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Verify Firebase Token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"idToken\": \"{{idToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "🔐 Flutter/mobile gets idToken from Firebase Auth SDK after sign-in.\nSend it here to verify + get Firestore profile.\n\nTo get idToken in Postman for testing:\n1. Use Firebase REST API: POST https://identitytoolkit.googleapis.com/v1/accounts:signInWithPassword?key=AIzaSy...\n   Body: { email, password, returnSecureToken: true }\n2. Copy idToken from response\n3. Paste into {{idToken}} variable"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile (Bearer Token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me",
            "description": "🔐 Protected. Requires: Authorization: Bearer <Firebase ID Token>\nReturns full user profile from Firestore."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User by UID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/user/{{userId}}",
            "description": "Get any user profile by Firebase UID."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Firebase Auth flow.\n\nSteps:\n1. Register with email+password → creates Firebase Auth user + Firestore profile\n2. Use Firebase client SDK to sign in → get idToken\n3. POST /login with idToken to verify + get profile\n4. Use idToken as Bearer token for all protected routes"
    },
    {
